{"word":"Chiding","slug":"chiding","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Chiding</b> Cain chides God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=14'>Gen 4:14</a><br/> Pharaoh chides Abraham, for calling his wife his sister<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=19'>Gen 12:19</a><br/> Abimelech chides Abraham for a like offense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=10'>Gen 20:10</a><br/> Abimelech chides Isaac for similar conduct<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=10'>Gen 26:10</a><br/> Isaac and Laban chide each other<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=42'>Gen 31:42</a><br/> Jacob chides Simeon and Levi for slaying Hamor and Shechem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=30'>Gen 34:30</a><br/> Reuben chides his brethren for their treatment of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=22'>Gen 42:22</a><br/> Israelites chide Moses and tempt God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=7'>Exo 17:7</a><br/> Deborah chides Israel in her epic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=5&verse=23'>Jdg 5:23</a><br/> David chides Joab for slaying Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=31'>2Sa 3:31</a><br/> Joab chides David for lamenting the death of Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=7'>2Sa 19:7</a><br/> Jesus chides his disciples:<br/> - On account of their unbelief<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=26'>Mat 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=31'>Mat 14:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=11'>Mat 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=17'>Mat 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=40'>Mar 4:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=25'>Luk 8:25</a> <br/> - For slowness of heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=16'>Mat 15:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=9'>Mat 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=11'>Mat 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=18'>Mar 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=25'>Luk 24:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=9'>Joh 14:9</a> <br/> - For sleeping in Gethsemane<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=40'>Mat 26:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=27'>Mar 14:27</a> <br/> - For forbidding children to be brought to him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=14'>Mat 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=14'>Mar 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=16'>Luk 18:16</a> "}]}